Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉如何？\N{\rEng}How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活着\N{\rEng}Alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到了什么？\N{\rEng}What do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.45,0:01:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色… 房间\N{\rEng}White... room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.73,0:01:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,座椅\N{\rEng}Chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.53,0:01:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛·布加迪设计的王座椅\N{\rEng}Carlo Bugatti throne chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.98,0:01:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钢琴\N{\rEng}Piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.92,0:01:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,施坦威牌大三角钢琴\N{\rEng}Stenway, cuts of grand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.71,0:01:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,画\N{\rEng}Art.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.59,0:01:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,《基督诞生》 皮埃罗·德拉·弗朗西斯卡\N{\rEng}The nativity, de Piero Della Francesca.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.51,0:01:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是你的父亲\N{\rEng}I am your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.81,0:01:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起来走走\N{\rEng}Ambulate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.56,0:02:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常好\N{\rEng}Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是吗？\N{\rEng}Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.72,0:02:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说完美？\N{\rEng}Perfect?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.87,0:02:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你儿子？\N{\rEng}Your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.93,0:02:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的创造物\N{\rEng}You are my creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.64,0:02:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字？\N{\rEng}What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.90,0:02:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大卫\N{\rEng}David.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你来弹首曲子吧\N{\rEng}Why don't you play something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想让我弹什么？\N{\rEng}What would you like me to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.70,0:02:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瓦格纳\N{\rEng}Wagner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.11,0:02:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪一首？\N{\rEng}Selection?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己选吧\N{\rEng}The oldest choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是众神进入英灵殿\N{\rEng}The entry of the Gods into Valhalla.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有乐队伴奏 略显单薄\N{\rEng}A little anemic, not the orchestra.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能问你个问题吗 父亲？\N{\rEng}May I ask you a question, father?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说\N{\rEng}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你创造了我\N{\rEng}If you created me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.53,0:03:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁创造了你？\N{\rEng}Who created you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千百年来的谜题\N{\rEng}The question of the ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望有一天你我能找到答案\N{\rEng}Which I hope you and I will answer one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.03,0:03:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一切\N{\rEng}All this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些精美的艺术品\N{\rEng}All these wonders of art
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,设计 人类的创造力\N{\rEng}design, human ingenuity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:03:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这个终极问题面前\N{\rEng}All utterly meaningless in the face of
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.14,0:04:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都可谓没有丝毫意义可言\N{\rEng}the only question that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们从何而来？\N{\rEng}Where do we come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不愿意相信\N{\rEng}I refuse to believe that man kind
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们人类不过是分子进化过程中偶然产生的副产品\N{\rEng}is a random by-product of molecular circumstance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.28,0:04:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不相信我们不过是生物学上的小概率事件\N{\rEng}No more than the result of Mere biological chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定不止如此\N{\rEng}There must be more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我和你 儿子\N{\rEng}And you and I, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.71,0:04:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们来解答\N{\rEng}We will find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.67,0:04:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么请允许我思考片刻\N{\rEng}Allow me then a moment to consider.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要找你的创造者 我正看着我的\N{\rEng}You seek your creator. I am looking at mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.87,0:04:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将侍奉你 但你是人类\N{\rEng}I will serve you. Yet you're human.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会死 但我不会\N{\rEng}You will die. I will not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.74,0:04:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我倒杯茶 大卫\N{\rEng}Bring me this tea, David.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我倒杯茶\N{\rEng}Bring me the tea.
