Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.97,0:06:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs20\an8\1c&HFFFFFF&}目的地：起源者6号行星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs20\an8\1c&HFFFFFF&}预计到达时间：7年4个月
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.61,0:06:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔特 进行能量网络充能的时间到了\N{\rEng}Walter, it's time to recharge the energy grid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请迅速前往舰桥\N{\rEng}Please report to the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就来 老妈\N{\rEng}On my way, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前正在展开充能帆板\N{\rEng}Deploying energy recharge cells now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帆板已就位 现在开始充能\N{\rEng}Cells deployed. Recharge commencing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs20\an8\1c&HFFFFFF&}船员：丹妮尔丝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七声钟响 一切正常\N{\rEng}Seven bells and all's well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs20\an8\1c&HFFFFFF&}海军值勤以钟响报时 七响钟代表以下时段\N[ 03:30 / 07:30 / 11:30 / 15:30 / 19:30 / 23:30 ]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs20\an8\1c&HFFFFFF&}舰长：布兰森
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船员检查完毕\N{\rEng}Crew checks complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.48,0:07:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使用新安全代码 31564-F\N{\rEng}New security Code 31564-F
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔特 我们有麻烦了\N{\rEng}Walter, we have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚在106扇区检测到一次中微子爆发\N{\rEng}A neutrino burst was detected in sector 106.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可能会引发灾难性后果\N{\rEng}This could trigger a destructive event.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你立刻前往舰桥\N{\rEng}Report to the bridge immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就来 老妈\N{\rEng}On my way, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警告 检测到能量骤增\N{\rEng}Warning, power surge detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老妈 快收起充能帆板\N{\rEng}Mother, retract the energy cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,启用所有备用能源\N{\rEng}And channel all useless power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.43,0:09:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紧急情况\N{\rEng}Emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威胁等级 危急\N{\rEng}Threat level: CRITICAL.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,启动紧急船员唤醒程序\N{\rEng}Initiate emergency crew revival.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请注意\N{\rEng}Attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.23,0:09:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有非必要人员 请迅速离开冬眠舱\N{\rEng}Non-essential personnel, evacuate the cryo chamber immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹妮尔丝 看着我 看着我\N{\rEng}Daniels! Look at me, look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.59,0:09:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要马上起来 好吗 我们要提前出来\N{\rEng}I need you to get up. Ok? We're coming up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改写紧急安全协议\N{\rEng}Override the SSP
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呼唤现在就打开冬眠舱\N{\rEng}And breach the chamber now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着我 没事的\N{\rEng}Look at me. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 嘿 快起来 起来\N{\rEng}Hey, hey, come on up. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 舰长\N{\rEng}Captain! Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雅各布 快起来\N{\rEng}Jacob! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.99,0:09:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 雅各布 - 别妨碍他们\N{\rEng}- Jake. - Let them work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雅各布 我的天啊\N{\rEng}Jake! Oh my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 丹妮尔斯 快走 - 雅各布 快起来\N{\rEng}- Daniels, come on! - Jake! Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 让他们来 - 雅各布\N{\rEng}- Let them work. - Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他们来 让他们来\N{\rEng}Let them work! Let them work!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 把它打开 - 快\N{\rEng}- Get it open! - Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雅各布 雅各布\N{\rEng}Jake! Jake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\rEng}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把她送到后边去 让她走开\N{\rEng}Get her out of there! Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退后\N{\rEng}Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.31,0:12:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 你在哪 我想你\N{\rEng}Hey! Where are you? I miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.18,0:12:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看我这边\N{\rEng}You take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 我知道 我说过要和你一起来的\N{\rEng}I know, I know. I said I wouldn't go without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你没事吧？- 没 没事\N{\rEng}- Are you alright? - Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看这个\N{\rEng}Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.28,0:12:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还是快点上来吧\N{\rEng}Now get your ass up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不能保证救你\N{\rEng}I can't make any promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.61,0:12:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你\N{\rEng}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是你的船员\N{\rEng}They're your crew now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们需要领导\N{\rEng}They need a leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你相信我 对吗？\N{\rEng}You believe in dream, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我来迟了 长官\N{\rEng}Sorry I'm late, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的\N{\rEng}No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道该怎么表达 所以我就直说吧\N{\rEng}I can't think of any other way to say it even... to say are we...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.67,0:13:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们遭受了惨痛的悲剧\N{\rEng}We suffered a... A monumental tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后我会尽我所能来\N{\rEng}And I'm gonna do the best that I can to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来接下雅各布的担子 以他为榜样 做好这个舰长\N{\rEng}live up to Jacob, his, fine example as your captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们将永远永远缅怀他\N{\rEng}But he, he will be sorely missed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我提前感谢大家的支持\N{\rEng}And I'm grateful in advance for your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们损失了47名殖民者\N{\rEng}So, we lost 47 colonists
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.42,0:13:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有16个二代胚胎\N{\rEng}and 16 second generation embryos
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.41,0:14:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及一名大家都认识的船员\N{\rEng}and, one, obviously one crew member.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外目前飞船船体的完整性稳定在83%\N{\rEng}The current structural integrity of the ship is holding at 83%
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我们有很多次级系统都处于离线状态\N{\rEng}but we have many secondary systems that are offline.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以这是怎么回事？\N{\rEng}So what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,附近的恒星耀斑引起了高能冲击波\N{\rEng}A highly charge shock wave from nearby stellar ignition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们当时展开了能量帆充能\N{\rEng}As the cells were deploying for recharge
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吸收了巨量冲击\N{\rEng}we absorbed the full burn of the storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔特\N{\rEng}And Walter
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.37,0:14:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你和老妈对核心代码进行彻彻底底的检查\N{\rEng}I will want you and mother time to go a complete
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彻底检查以帮助我们找到\N{\rEng}core code review so that we can understand
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这场事故发生的根源\N{\rEng}how's those happened in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是个局部随机事件 长官\N{\rEng}It was a random localized event, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们无法检测到自然发生的恒星耀斑 也无法预警\N{\rEng}There is no way to detect spontaneous stellar flares until it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们运气差\N{\rEng}It was bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.57,0:14:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着 法里斯 我不相信运气\N{\rEng}Alright, Faris, I don't believe in luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对运气没兴趣\N{\rEng}I'm not interested in luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.50,0:14:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我更希望我们可以更能干\N{\rEng}I prefer that we be more capable
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备更足 不靠运气 而是靠观察 思考 信仰和决心\N{\rEng}and prepared than lucky. Observation, reflection, faith and determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样我们才有可能探明前方那条漫长未知的路\N{\rEng}In this way we may navigate the path as it unfolds before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.56,0:14:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吗 我们是还有\N{\rEng}Alright? We have what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概八个充电周期的路才能到达欧瑞伽6号吗？\N{\rEng}Eight more recharge cycles to go before we get to Origae-6?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:14:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你在问我吗 长官？- 是的 沃尔特 我在问你\N{\rEng}- Is that a question, sir? - Yes, Walter, that's a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:14:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说的对\N{\rEng}That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.59,0:15:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们先把飞船修好 好吗\N{\rEng}So...let's get this ship fixed.. Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.89,0:15:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们就开工吧\N{\rEng}Let's uh, let's get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.99,0:15:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长官 等一下\N{\rEng}Sir, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 长官 - 你说\N{\rEng}- Sir. - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.61,0:15:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们失去了47名殖民者 以及我们的舰长\N{\rEng}We just lost 47 colonists and our captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要进行哀悼\N{\rEng}We need to acknowledge that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很明白你的心情\N{\rEng}I completely understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果不及时修好船\N{\rEng}But if we don't make these repairs
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就会失去所有殖民者\N{\rEng}We will lose all the colonists.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.64,0:15:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 但我们应该为巴拉森舰长做点什么\N{\rEng}Yeah, we should do something for Captain Branson at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.85,0:15:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这件事情没有商量 田纳西\N{\rEng}This is not a discussion. Tennessee.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.15,0:15:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整地模块已经稳定了\N{\rEng}The terraforming module is stable
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但连接支架受了点损伤\N{\rEng}but the connecting struts took some damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.57,0:15:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还得去检查车辆\N{\rEng}I still need to check the vehicles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你\N{\rEng}I can help
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你愿意的话\N{\rEng}if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.06,0:15:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.21,0:15:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔特 你预计需要多久才能再次进行速航？\N{\rEng}Walter, How long do you predict before we can make our next jump?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.81,0:15:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成修理大概需要48小时\N{\rEng}Repairs should take approximately 48 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.25,0:16:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们应该尽快撤出这个区域\N{\rEng}But we should make an effort to vacate the sector
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以防后续耀斑\N{\rEng}in case of after flares.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.96,0:16:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我完全同意\N{\rEng}Absolutely agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.39,0:16:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们开工吧 解散吧 谢谢\N{\rEng}So let's get to work ok? Dismissed. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C62号门已开启\N{\rEng}C-62 open.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.81,0:16:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关闭C62号 打开17号空气阀\N{\rEng}Seal C-62. Open Airlock 17.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打开整地舱舱门\N{\rEng}Open door to terraforming bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.29,0:16:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死\N{\rEng}Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,张力下降了15%\N{\rEng}Tensions are 15% down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉紧\N{\rEng}Arming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.39,0:16:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以了\N{\rEng}Secured.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到了\N{\rEng}Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想来这\N{\rEng}Wasn't my idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雅各布梦想着我们在新世界造一间小木屋\N{\rEng}Jake have this dream of us building a cabin on the new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做两个拓荒者\N{\rEng}Like pioneers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,木屋建在湖畔\N{\rEng}A cabin on a lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欧瑞伽6号的殖民区域内刚好有个湖\N{\rEng}There is a lake in the terraforming zone on Origae-6.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说的是真正的木头做的木屋\N{\rEng}I mean a real cabin made of real wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以飞船上载了建造木屋要用的木料\N{\rEng}So in the ship storage, there's enough wood to build a cabin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.26,0:17:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有斧子 锯子和金属钉子\N{\rEng}Axes and saws and metal nails
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些东西我完全都不会用\N{\rEng}I don't have a clue what to do with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.08,0:17:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些东西\N{\rEng}All this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.91,0:17:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了开始新生活\N{\rEng}to start our new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.96,0:17:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在看来这是何苦呢\N{\rEng}Now I wonder, why bother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因为你们说过要在湖边建一间木屋\N{\rEng}Because you promised to build a log cabin on a lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他最爱这个\N{\rEng}This was his favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.89,0:18:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是个有品位的人\N{\rEng}A man of taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样喝\N{\rEng}Straight up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.82,0:18:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不加冰 不加水 不加淡酒\N{\rEng}No ice, no water, no chaser.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.77,0:18:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都不加\N{\rEng}No shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.35,0:18:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔特\N{\rEng}Walter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,入乡随俗\N{\rEng}When in Rome
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬那些英年早逝的好人们\N{\rEng}To all the good people gone to soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永远铭记他们\N{\rEng}May we remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永远铭记\N{\rEng}Remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯\N{\rEng}Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.88,0:19:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们公然违抗我的命令\N{\rEng}They disobeyed a direct order.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她只是安葬了她丈夫\N{\rEng}She buried her husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 凯瑞 不是那样的 他们不信任我\N{\rEng}No, Karine, it's not that. They don't trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而他们不信任我的理由\N{\rEng}And they don't trust me for the same reason
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与公司不让我负责这次任务的理由一样\N{\rEng}the company didn't trust me to lead this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们认为我有宗教信仰\N{\rEng}Because you can't be a person of faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.48,0:19:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就肯定没办法做出正确的 理智的决定\N{\rEng}And be counted on to make qualified rational decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觉得我是个极端份子 说白了 就是个疯子\N{\rEng}You're an extremist. You know, you're a lunatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.71,0:19:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我们到达目的地以后\N{\rEng}When we get to where we're going
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些人就不再是你的手下了 而是你的邻居\N{\rEng}This people won't be your crew anymore. They will be your neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.68,0:19:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可别忘了\N{\rEng}Remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.23,0:20:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对他们友善点 好吗\N{\rEng}Tread softly, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.51,0:20:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法里斯 能听到吗？\N{\rEng}Faris, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.22,0:20:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到了\N{\rEng}Copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.42,0:20:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那开始吧\N{\rEng}Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.51,0:20:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老天呐 你们看看这景色\N{\rEng}Damn, y'all should see this view.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.00,0:20:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你修好摄像机阵列之前 我们什么也看不到\N{\rEng}We can't see anything until you get the camera ring fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.26,0:20:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会从窗户里往外看吗\N{\rEng}Why don't you look out the damn window, hon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安哥 快点 我们赶紧恢复电源\N{\rEng}Ankor, come on, let's get this power back up,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样他们就可以欣赏这美景了\N{\rEng}so these people can enjoy the beautiful view.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.35,0:20:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就位\N{\rEng}Almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.76,0:20:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 安哥 就位之后通知我一下\N{\rEng}Alright, Ankor, let me know when you're in a position.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.78,0:20:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们就开始干活吧\N{\rEng}We can get this party started.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.72,0:20:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就位了\N{\rEng}I'm in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,断开缆绳\N{\rEng}Contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都顺利吗\N{\rEng}All good, Tee?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.91,0:21:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很顺利 搞定\N{\rEng}Alright, we are clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收起来\N{\rEng}Reel her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.32,0:21:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题\N{\rEng}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.49,0:21:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在启动绞盘\N{\rEng}Winch engaging, Tee.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.82,0:21:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帆板收起\N{\rEng}Reeling her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.76,0:21:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太顺利了\N{\rEng}Working like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.09,0:21:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞定了\N{\rEng}There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.38,0:21:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摄像系统恢复\N{\rEng}And we are back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:21:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干得好 田纳西\N{\rEng}Well done Tee.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.83,0:21:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们连上系统了\N{\rEng}We're alive down here,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.21,0:21:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回来吧\N{\rEng}come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.51,0:21:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可别丢下我跑了\N{\rEng}Don't leave without me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们丢下他走人 怎么样 长官\N{\rEng}Permission to leave without him, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.66,0:22:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 丹妮\N{\rEng}Welcome back, Danny.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.81,0:22:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 我这边收工了\N{\rEng}Alright, that's me done, Tee.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.42,0:22:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我跟着你回去\N{\rEng}Alright, I'm following you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.33,0:22:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦给辛苦异常的我准备好冰镇啤酒\N{\rEng}Please have a cold beer ready for the weary traveler.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.18,0:22:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题亲爱的 我跟你一起喝一杯\N{\rEng}You got it, darling. I will draw circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.47,0:22:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法瑞丝 你把那个...\N{\rEng}Faris, Faris? Put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.16,0:22:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们刚才 看到了吗\N{\rEng}What the.. Did you guys just see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.14,0:22:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他刚说什么?\N{\rEng}What did he just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.62,0:22:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,田纳西 你能听到吗？\N{\rEng}Tennessee, do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.24,0:22:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,田纳西 能听到吗？\N{\rEng}Tennessee, can you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.92,0:22:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,田纳西 你没事吧？\N{\rEng}Tennessee. You alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.00,0:22:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么鬼东西\N{\rEng}What in the fuck was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.17,0:22:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 回去了 我这就回去了\N{\rEng}I don't know. Coming in. I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.99,0:23:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个很有可能是外星信号\N{\rEng}A rogue transmission loss, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.08,0:23:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的头盔能收到 是因为你漂得太远\N{\rEng}Your helmet must have picked it up because you were so far out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.35,0:23:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超出了通讯缓冲器范围\N{\rEng}Past our communication buffers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.90,0:23:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有音频吗 老妈\N{\rEng}Is there audio, Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.35,0:23:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在整理 请稍候\N{\rEng}Collating. A moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.19,0:23:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经重整了这段信号 奥姆舰长\N{\rEng}I reoriented the transmission, Captain Oram.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.20,0:23:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是回波 我们的仪器受损不小\N{\rEng}Gotta be an echo, instruments took a lot of damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.41,0:23:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们到这后 它每隔46秒出现一次\N{\rEng}Been happening every 46 seconds ever since we got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.20,0:23:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是约翰·丹佛的歌吗\N{\rEng}That's fucking John Denver.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.00,0:23:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是 "乡村路带我回家"\N{\rEng}That's "Take Me Home, Country Roads".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.49,0:23:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你开玩笑吧\N{\rEng}You gotta be kiddin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.75,0:24:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 不 我从来不拿丹佛开玩笑\N{\rEng}No, I never kid about John Denver.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.11,0:24:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信号里还有定位数据\N{\rEng}There is geometric data too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.98,0:24:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老妈 请查一下信号的发射源\N{\rEng}Mother, please track the signal to its source.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.10,0:24:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在查找\N{\rEng}Working.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.12,0:24:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信号源已经成功定位\N{\rEng}Source of transmission located.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.29,0:24:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发现该信号来自87号扇区\N{\rEng}Signal originates in the sector 87.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.48,0:24:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,具体位置赤经47.6度\N{\rEng}Right ascension 47.6
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.40,0:24:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是位于我们当前位置下方24.3度\N{\rEng}and a declination of 24.3 from our current location.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.35,0:24:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一颗主序恒星 就像我们的太阳\N{\rEng}She appears to be a main sequence star lot like our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.85,0:24:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比太阳更古老\N{\rEng}But old, very old.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.87,0:24:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有五颗行星\N{\rEng}Five planets.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.01,0:24:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你们看\N{\rEng}Wait. Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.07,0:24:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第四颗行星\N{\rEng}Planet number four.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.83,0:24:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第四颗行星正处在宜居带上\N{\rEng}The planet number four is square in a habitable zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.43,0:24:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很符合我们的要求\N{\rEng}Prime candidate, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.43,0:25:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行星地表重力是0.96G 有海洋和陆地\N{\rEng}0.96 G's at surface, oceans, land mass.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.27,0:25:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常有可能存在生态圈\N{\rEng}High likely hood of a living biosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.30,0:25:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比我们对欧瑞伽6号最乐观的预测还要好\N{\rEng}That's beyond the most optimistic projections of Oriage-6.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.41,0:25:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前怎么没发现 整个扇区都扫描过\N{\rEng}How did we miss this? We scanned the entire sector.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.69,0:25:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里克斯 离我们多远\N{\rEng}Ricks, how far is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.86,0:25:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常近\N{\rEng}She's close.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.83,0:25:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,启动速航 几周就到\N{\rEng}Little jump. A few weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.09,0:25:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们甚至不需要回去冬眠\N{\rEng}Wouldn't even have to go back into hyper sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.12,0:25:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们去欧瑞伽6号需要多久呢\N{\rEng}And how long is it gonna take to get to Origae-6?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.94,0:25:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要7年4个月\N{\rEng}Seven years, four months.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.93,0:25:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话我们可是要睡很久啊\N{\rEng}That's one hell of a sleep cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.83,0:25:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长官 我相信这里没人愿意\N{\rEng}Sir, I think it's safe to say that none of us are too keen
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.57,0:25:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再回到冬眠舱里了\N{\rEng}on getting back to one of those pods.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.30,0:25:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许我们应该近距离观察一下\N{\rEng}Maybe we need to, um... Take a closer look.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.60,0:25:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人反对吗\N{\rEng}Any objections?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.15,0:25:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那好 里克斯 我们...\N{\rEng}Okay, Ricks, let's..
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.02,0:25:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们改变航线 近距离观察一下\N{\rEng}Let's try to course and take a closer look.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.17,0:25:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 长官\N{\rEng}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.78,0:26:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 能聊几句吗？\N{\rEng}Captain, can I talk to you for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.40,0:26:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你确定要这样吗\N{\rEng}Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.40,0:26:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想说什么\N{\rEng}How do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.52,0:26:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们花了十年寻找欧瑞伽6号\N{\rEng}We've spent a decade searching for Origae-6.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.82,0:26:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做过调查 做过模拟试验 绘制过地形图\N{\rEng}We vetted it, we ran the simulations, we mapped the terrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.24,0:26:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们为它接受训练 - 我明白\N{\rEng}- It's what we trained for. - I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.92,0:26:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而现在要抛开这些\N{\rEng}And now we're gonna scrap all that
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.49,0:26:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去追踪一个外星信号吗\N{\rEng}to chase a rogue transmission?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.82,0:26:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想想吧\N{\rEng}Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.04,0:26:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在不可能有人类的星球上 出现一个人\N{\rEng}A human being out there where there can't be any humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.96,0:26:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个隐藏的星球莫名其妙地出现\N{\rEng}A hidden planet that turns up out of nowhere
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.84,0:26:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还碰巧符合我们所有的要求 哪有这么好的事啊\N{\rEng}And just happens to be perfect for us. It's too good to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.02,0:26:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有这么好的事 你什么意思\N{\rEng}Too good to be true? What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.28,0:26:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说谁知道那有什么\N{\rEng}We don't know what the fuck's out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.84,0:26:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许只是以前没发现它 丹妮\N{\rEng}Maybe we just missed the planet, Danny.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.17,0:26:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可这个风险实在是太大了 根本就不值得去冒\N{\rEng}This is a monumental risk not worth taking.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.09,0:26:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有定死走哪条路啊\N{\rEng}I'm not committing to anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.65,0:26:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想根据具体情况随机应变做出选择\N{\rEng}I'm simply trying to navigate the path as it unfolds before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.77,0:26:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这颗星球很有潜力\N{\rEng}And this has the potential
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.17,0:26:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成为更适合我们居住的殖民地\N{\rEng}to be a better habitat for a colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.86,0:26:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 它是有潜力 但我们不确定\N{\rEng}It has the potential. We don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.61,0:26:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有船员们 没有人\N{\rEng}By the way, this crew nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.08,0:26:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人愿意再回到冬眠舱了\N{\rEng}Nobody wants to get back in the pods.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.20,0:27:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吗\N{\rEng}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.01,0:27:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且那个信号里 有人类的声音\N{\rEng}And that was a human voice in that transmission,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.50,0:27:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 我们就有责任去调查一下\N{\rEng}And it's our responsibility to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.29,0:27:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们真正的责任是保护契约号飞船上的两千名殖民者\N{\rEng}It's our responsibility to protect the 2,000 colonists on this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.53,0:27:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是在徒手攀岩\N{\rEng}I'm not free climbing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.92,0:27:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要绳索 我也在用绳索\N{\rEng}I need ropes, and I'm using ropes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.60,0:27:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是是基于目前所有的信息而做出的最佳选择\N{\rEng}This is good judgment, based on all the data available.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.29,0:27:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吗？\N{\rEng}You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.57,0:27:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为副舰长 我提出抗议 正式抗议\N{\rEng}As your second I need to protest. Officially.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.32,0:27:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正式抗议\N{\rEng}Officially?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.63,0:27:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 丹妮 我记到航行日志里\N{\rEng}Okay, Danny. I'll put it in the log.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.89,0:27:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以出去了\N{\rEng}You're dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.25,0:28:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我搜遍了全部频段\N{\rEng}I'm cycling through every channel
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.60,0:28:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只搜到了一堆干扰和白噪声\N{\rEng}but we're getting a lot of interference and white noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.99,0:28:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有一些高频段回声\N{\rEng}Some high frequency echos.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.29,0:28:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那听到什么了吗？\N{\rEng}Do you hear anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.59,0:28:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我们的幽灵朋友发出的持续信号\N{\rEng}Just the continuing signal from our friendly ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.54,0:28:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先让飞船进入轨道吧\N{\rEng}Let's bring us in the closer orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.90,0:28:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备好登陆舱\N{\rEng}And prepare the lander.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.44,0:28:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改变船体角度 启用循环燃烧系统\N{\rEng}Rolling progress, commencing circular location berm.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.49,0:28:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毒素水平在可接受范围内\N{\rEng}Tox levels, withing tolerances.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.42,0:28:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里的电离层活动很强\N{\rEng}It's one hell of a strong ionosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.98,0:28:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我看到了\N{\rEng}Yeah, I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.27,0:28:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还没坐过登陆舱吧\N{\rEng}Hey, you ever done lander drop before?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.72,0:28:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一边去\N{\rEng}Fuck you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.02,0:28:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法瑞丝 热层里面有一场电磁风暴\N{\rEng}Faris, looks like a plasma storm in the thermosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.49,0:28:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,风速大概是每小时250公里\N{\rEng}We got something like 250 kph.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.60,0:29:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那要飞过去肯定够我们受的\N{\rEng}That's gonna be a motherfucker to fly through.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.77,0:29:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 恐怕真是这样\N{\rEng}Yes, I'm afraid so.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.61,0:29:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果风暴磁性增强 通讯可能会不稳定\N{\rEng}Communication will be spotty if the storm is electromagnetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.51,0:29:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能安全着陆吗\N{\rEng}It will be safe to land?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.96,0:29:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那得看你觉得什么叫安全\N{\rEng}Depends on what you call safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.13,0:29:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒计时二十秒\N{\rEng}T minus Twenty seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.27,0:29:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备发射吧\N{\rEng}So let her rip.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.47,0:29:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题\N{\rEng}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.58,0:29:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在启用轨道模式前往信号源上空\N{\rEng}Preparing for orbital mode over signal position.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.18,0:29:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在 老妈 麻烦和我同步启动程序\N{\rEng}Now, Mother, please coordinate lock sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.01,0:29:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到\N{\rEng}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.32,0:29:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,登陆舱1号可以发射\N{\rEng}You're clear to launch Lander one.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.68,0:29:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我们走吧 发射\N{\rEng}Alright, here we go. Launching.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.73,0:29:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒数 三\N{\rEng}Together. Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.45,0:29:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二\N{\rEng}Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.65,0:29:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一\N{\rEng}One.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.63,0:29:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,登陆舱1号已分离\N{\rEng}Lander run released.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.28,0:29:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们出发了\N{\rEng}And away they go.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.60,0:29:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从这上面看真壮观 法瑞丝\N{\rEng}Looking gorgeous from up here Faris.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.88,0:29:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还好是你在开 不是你家老田\N{\rEng}It's a good thing you're driving and not the old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.28,0:29:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 我到底哪里老了 奶糖妹\N{\rEng}Hey, little less to the old man, sweet tits.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.21,0:29:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 注意点\N{\rEng}Hey, language, language.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.81,0:29:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 放尊重点 棒棒糖 - 我听到了\N{\rEng}- Be respectful there, sugerdad. - I can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.29,0:29:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她先说的\N{\rEng}She started it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.30,0:30:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里克斯想的话 也可以谈论你的胸部\N{\rEng}Ricks can talk about your tits, if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.12,0:30:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是铁哥们\N{\rEng}Some's very secured in our relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.15,0:30:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我表示很满意\N{\rEng}I deal with my wife's tits.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.41,0:30:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都专心工作吧\N{\rEng}Let's maintain focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.21,0:30:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们那边顺利吗\N{\rEng}Everything looking good down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.25,0:30:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 一切顺利\N{\rEng}Yeah, we are good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.35,0:30:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,预计5分钟后进入散逸层\N{\rEng}Expect to hit exosphere in five.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.85,0:30:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后面的坐稳了 一会儿就要颠簸了\N{\rEng}You might wanna hold on back there. It's about to get rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.50,0:30:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌太空\N{\rEng}I hate space.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.12,0:30:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以说你应该练练瑜伽\N{\rEng}This is why you need to do yoga.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.84,0:30:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 撑住 法瑞丝 - 我来了\N{\rEng}- Hold it, Faris. - I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.39,0:30:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法瑞丝\N{\rEng}Faris.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.15,0:30:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能恢复吗\N{\rEng}Can you get her up?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.54,0:30:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通讯断了\N{\rEng}We lost comm.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.27,0:30:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 见鬼\N{\rEng}Oh shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.56,0:30:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3号 4号引擎故障\N{\rEng}Failure in thrusters three and four.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.58,0:30:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你能行吗 - 能行\N{\rEng}- You got it? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.10,0:30:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能行 你别再问我行不行了 我肯定行\N{\rEng}Stop asking if I've got it, I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.71,0:31:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞定了\N{\rEng}Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.48,0:31:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,见鬼\N{\rEng}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.30,0:31:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大伙儿都好吗？\N{\rEng}You guys alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.51,0:31:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.51,0:31:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,着陆传感器已启动\N{\rEng}Landing sensors engaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.40,0:31:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢这地形\N{\rEng}I don't like this terrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.43,0:31:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那面的水面还算平静\N{\rEng}We got smooth water over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.35,0:31:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我要在水面上降落 - 好的\N{\rEng}- I'm gonna put us down amphib. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.36,0:32:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已着陆\N{\rEng}Contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.23,0:32:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引擎关闭\N{\rEng}Engines stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.36,0:32:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在进行着陆\N{\rEng}We're down.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.54,0:32:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打开安全护栏\N{\rEng}Bars.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.64,0:32:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1号 能收到吗？\N{\rEng}Lander one, are you reading me?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.01,0:32:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到了 刚才的着陆太惊险了\N{\rEng}Roger that, that was one hell of a landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.77,0:32:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我们这里听不太清\N{\rEng}Yeah, we are having some trouble reading you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.57,0:32:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们能不能想办法增强信号？\N{\rEng}Is there anyway you can try to boost the signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.48,0:32:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在水上着陆时 可能撞上了什么东西\N{\rEng}We may have hit something when we were down in water.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.35,0:32:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能听到吗 我现在要去检查一下船体\N{\rEng}If you can hear me, I am gonna go, check up
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.24,0:32:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有损坏 然后去检查上行线路\N{\rEng}damage in the hull plates and then I will check the uplink.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.76,0:32:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 随时通报情况 完毕\N{\rEng}Alright, let me know how it looks. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.58,0:32:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在确认该行星大气成分\N{\rEng}Confirming atmospheric composition.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.51,0:32:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿好 大块头\N{\rEng}Here you go, big guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.63,0:32:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,氧气含量19.5%\N{\rEng}Oxygen, 19.5%.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.67,0:32:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安哥\N{\rEng}Ankor.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.97,0:32:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,氮气含量79.4%\N{\rEng}Nitrogen, 79.4%.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.70,0:32:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科尔\N{\rEng}Cole.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.35,0:32:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗西\N{\rEng}Rosie.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.35,0:32:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大气历力 每平方英寸15.4磅\N{\rEng}Barometric Pressure 15.4 PSI.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.02,0:32:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莱沃德\N{\rEng}Ledward.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.12,0:32:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 准备好了吗\N{\rEng}Everyone set?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.07,0:33:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出发吧 开始行动了\N{\rEng}Let's go, let's move guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.28,0:33:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 走吧 伙计们 - 空气不错\N{\rEng}- Come on guys. - The air feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.77,0:33:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法瑞丝 能听到吗？\N{\rEng}Faris, if you got me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.20,0:33:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 能 非常清楚 - 很清楚 长官\N{\rEng}- Yeah, loud and clear. - All clear Serg.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.54,0:33:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 从现在开始 我们必须按照安全守则行事\N{\rEng}Okay, we are gonna keep expedition's security protocols in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.80,0:33:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记得锁好各个舱门 懂吗\N{\rEng}Keep those doors locked and sealed. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.75,0:33:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到 遵命\N{\rEng}Yeah. Copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.84,0:33:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧\N{\rEng}Will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.14,0:33:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩得开心\N{\rEng}Y'all have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.21,0:33:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔特 我们还得走多远\N{\rEng}Walter, how far do we have to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.78,0:33:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信号源头位于西方8公里外\N{\rEng}The signal source is 8 km west
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.73,0:33:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那里的海拔比较高\N{\rEng}but at considerable elevation.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.73,0:33:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛普中士\N{\rEng}Sergeant Lope.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.36,0:33:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们去找那个幽灵\N{\rEng}Let's go find our ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.58,0:34:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里很适合建木屋\N{\rEng}Nice place for a log cabin.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.77,0:34:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雅各布肯定会喜欢\N{\rEng}Jake would have loved this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.28,0:34:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 丹妮\N{\rEng}Hey, Danny.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.00,0:34:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我选择这个地方还算不错是吧\N{\rEng}It's not such a bad landing site after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.59,0:34:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以把居住区造在那边\N{\rEng}We get the housing units right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.17,0:34:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,民用设施建在河流对岸\N{\rEng}Civic complex beyond the berm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.29,0:34:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以就近取水了\N{\rEng}We've got access to fresh water.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.45,0:34:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没准可以在这里建立一个殖民地\N{\rEng}We might have a spot for colony right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.56,0:34:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再看看\N{\rEng}We'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.80,0:34:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 你这人真是太没信心了\N{\rEng}Oh, woman... yay of little faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.94,0:34:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他真是让人受不了\N{\rEng}He is insufferable.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.70,0:34:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高兴起来更讨厌 对吧\N{\rEng}It's worse when he's happy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.81,0:34:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是小麦啊\N{\rEng}This is wheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.35,0:34:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信我 我认得小麦\N{\rEng}Believe me, I know wheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.21,0:34:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很老 但是是人工种植的\N{\rEng}This is old, but definitely cultivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.45,0:35:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在地球外发现人类农作物的几率有多大\N{\rEng}What are the odds of finding human vegetation this far from Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.24,0:35:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,微乎其微\N{\rEng}Very unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.08,0:35:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁种的\N{\rEng}Who planted it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.10,0:35:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧\N{\rEng}Eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.24,0:35:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 宝贝 试试阿尔法\N{\rEng}Hey babe, try alpha.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.50,0:35:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 阿尔法开启\N{\rEng}Alright, Alpha's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.54,0:35:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没信号 试试贝塔频道\N{\rEng}Nothing, give beta a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.90,0:35:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贝塔线路\N{\rEng}Beta.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.47,0:35:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 还是没信号\N{\rEng}That's not doing shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.42,0:35:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天呐 真没办法增强信号了吗\N{\rEng}How's there really no way to boost the signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.66,0:35:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以关闭系统 重新对电池进行充能\N{\rEng}Not without going offline and recycling the cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.61,0:35:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那要花多少时间\N{\rEng}How long is that gonna take?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.80,0:36:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 几个小时\N{\rEng}I don't know. Few hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.32,0:36:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 大家跟上 快点 别掉队 - 加点小心\N{\rEng}- Keep up the pace. Take low. - Careful guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.74,0:36:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯\N{\rEng}Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.04,0:36:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\rEng}Hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.24,0:36:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打算就留在这里\N{\rEng}I think I want to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.04,0:36:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这里应该很适合进行生态研究\N{\rEng}This might be a good place to start a full ecology workup.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.15,0:36:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们回去时把我叫上 好吗\N{\rEng}You could pick me up on the way back ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.26,0:36:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中士\N{\rEng}Sergeant?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.26,0:36:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行行 没问题 莱沃德 你陪着凯瑞\N{\rEng}Yeah yeah that's right. Ledward, stay with Karine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.35,0:36:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4小时后在这里见 别关通讯\N{\rEng}Meet back here in four hours. Keep your comm open.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.06,0:36:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我老婆在一起的时候老实点\N{\rEng}Behave yourself with my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.28,0:36:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 舰长\N{\rEng}You got it, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.83,0:36:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\rEng}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.60,0:36:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有东西朝上面飞过\N{\rEng}Something passed over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.24,0:36:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把树冠都刮掉了\N{\rEng}Cut the tops off the trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.30,0:36:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那东西相当大\N{\rEng}Well, it had to be huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.29,0:36:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 不管是什么东西\N{\rEng}Well, Whatever it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.85,0:36:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都在上面\N{\rEng}It's up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.82,0:37:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吗\N{\rEng}You hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.55,0:37:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.33,0:37:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太安静了\N{\rEng}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.68,0:37:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有鸟叫 没有动物声音\N{\rEng}No birds, no animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.72,0:37:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都没有\N{\rEng}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.85,0:37:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 慢一点\N{\rEng}Wait, slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.82,0:37:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.47,0:37:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里不错啊\N{\rEng}This will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.98,0:37:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,探险小队 可以听到吗\N{\rEng}Expedition team, do we read us?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.94,0:37:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老妈说电磁风暴越来越强了\N{\rEng}Mother saying the ion storm is getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.56,0:37:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们很难定位到你们的位置\N{\rEng}We're having a hell of time tracking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.87,0:37:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经非常接近那个目标了\N{\rEng}We are getting very close... Target.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.57,0:37:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我们到了 再通话 好吗...\N{\rEng}Stay awake when we get there ok? Copy that?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.59,0:37:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真见鬼\N{\rEng}Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.56,0:38:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P3号\N{\rEng}P three.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.22,0:38:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去方便一下\N{\rEng}I gotta take a leak.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.50,0:38:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别太久了\N{\rEng}Don't be long.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.41,0:39:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莱沃德\N{\rEng}Leward?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.74,0:39:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了\N{\rEng}Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.72,0:39:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么鬼东西\N{\rEng}What the fuck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.84,0:39:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来好像是某种飞行器\N{\rEng}It appears to be some kind of vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.33,0:40:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安哥 科尔 守在这\N{\rEng}Ankor, Cole. Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.96,0:40:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 明白 - 遵命\N{\rEng}- You got it. - Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.62,0:40:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家小心 注意脚下\N{\rEng}Careful guys, watch your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.67,0:40:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你找到信号源了吗 沃尔特？- 走这边\N{\rEng}- We got a lock on the transmission Walter? - This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.01,0:40:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还不走 别掉队\N{\rEng}Let's go. Stick together.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.18,0:40:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这什么东西？\N{\rEng}Seeing this shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.66,0:40:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆\N{\rEng}Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.76,0:41:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走了 跟紧\N{\rEng}Come on, keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.86,0:41:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了 我就来\N{\rEng}Alright, I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.03,0:41:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧\N{\rEng}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.43,0:41:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事 没事 我没事\N{\rEng}Yeah, yeah, I am fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.85,0:41:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天哪\N{\rEng}God!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.40,0:41:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是巨人吧\N{\rEng}They were giants.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.24,0:41:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实 至少是巨人的雕像\N{\rEng}At least statues of giants.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.31,0:41:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊丽·肖博士\N{\rEng}"Dr. E. Shaw".
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.48,0:41:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊丽莎白·肖博士\N{\rEng}Dr. Elizabeth Shaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.73,0:41:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是普罗米修斯号上的首席科学家\N{\rEng}She was the chief science officer of the "Prometheus".
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.77,0:42:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那艘失踪的飞船\N{\rEng}The ship that disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.95,0:42:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错 10年前\N{\rEng}Precisely, ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.63,0:42:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,维兰德公司的船\N{\rEng}Weyland Industries.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.92,0:42:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是维兰德公司的\N{\rEng}This isn't a Weyland ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.09,0:42:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肖博士\N{\rEng}Dr. Shaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.48,0:42:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她怎么会死在这？\N{\rEng}How did she end up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.05,0:42:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 洛普中士 能帮我照一下吗？- 好的\N{\rEng}- Sergeant. Lope, can I get a light on this? -  Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.27,0:42:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 在这 - 小心点 好吗\N{\rEng}- Over here. - Be careful. Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.43,0:42:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老天\N{\rEng}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.47,0:42:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥姆 奥姆你后面 小心\N{\rEng}Oram, Oram behind you, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.02,0:43:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是信号源了\N{\rEng}I think we found our source.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.27,0:43:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肖博士来这里做什么\N{\rEng}What the hell was she doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.36,0:43:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可怜\N{\rEng}Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.39,0:43:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得坐会\N{\rEng}I have to sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.01,0:43:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 我得坐会\N{\rEng}I had to sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.41,0:43:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 我真的很抱歉\N{\rEng}I am sorry. I am so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.91,0:43:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不知道 - 我不知道我怎么了\N{\rEng}- I don't know. - what's wrong with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.43,0:43:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛看着我 看着我\N{\rEng}Look at me, look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.77,0:43:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没法呼吸\N{\rEng}I can't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.54,0:43:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别害怕\N{\rEng}Stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.18,0:43:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我马上回来\N{\rEng}I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.19,0:43:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥姆舰长 请回话\N{\rEng}Captain Oram. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.44,0:43:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请回话 克里斯 我是凯瑞 请回话\N{\rEng}Come in. Hey Chris, It's Karine. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.66,0:43:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么 我在\N{\rEng}What? Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.68,0:43:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边出了状况\N{\rEng}We have an issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.29,0:43:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在回登陆舱 重复 我们正在回登陆舱\N{\rEng}We're heading back to lander. I repeat, we are returning to the lander.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.76,0:43:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切还好吗\N{\rEng}Is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.52,0:44:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莱沃德生病了 我们正在往回走\N{\rEng}Ledward is sick. We're heading back.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.55,0:44:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法瑞丝 收到了吗 准备好医疗舱好吗\N{\rEng}Faris, you get that? Prep the med bay okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.16,0:44:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 凯瑞 出什么事了？\N{\rEng}Will do, Karine, What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.80,0:44:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 做好准备 我们很快就到\N{\rEng}Please just do it. We'll be there soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.14,0:44:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹妮 请回话\N{\rEng}Daniels come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.59,0:44:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要回去了\N{\rEng}We are heading back.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.15,0:44:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 出什么事了？- 不清楚\N{\rEng}- What's going on? - I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.46,0:44:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莱沃德好像出事了\N{\rEng}It's uh.. something about Ledward.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.01,0:44:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们来了 我们走\N{\rEng}They're coming. Let's move.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.35,0:44:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 伙计们 - 汤姆\N{\rEng}- Guys! - Tom!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.05,0:44:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 伙计 嘿 你没事吧\N{\rEng}What's going on man? Hey, You alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.25,0:44:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 说话呀 嘿 看着我 - 安哥 科尔\N{\rEng}- Talk to me. Hey, Look at me. - Ankor, Cole.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.46,0:44:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你没事吧？- 没 我没事\N{\rEng}- You alright? - Yeah, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.51,0:44:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你能走吗？- 能\N{\rEng}- Can you walk? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.61,0:44:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 我们走 赶紧离开这鬼地方\N{\rEng}Okay, let's go. Let's get the fuck out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.98,0:44:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\rEng}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.12,0:44:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 宝贝 你... 你这是要启动隔离程序吗\N{\rEng}Babe, are we talking quarantine protocols?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.16,0:44:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我我... 我不知道 但她说莱沃德正在出血\N{\rEng}I don't...I don't know, she said that Leward was bleeding
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.12,0:44:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我准备好治疗舱\N{\rEng}and to prepare the med bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.99,0:44:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出血\N{\rEng}Bleeding?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.75,0:44:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 好吧 我觉得得处理\N{\rEng}Yeah I know. That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.70,0:44:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法瑞丝 信号太差了 我们听不到 你再说一遍\N{\rEng}Faris, you're breaking up. We can't hear you. Can you repeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.44,0:45:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道怎么回事 我不知道有多严重\N{\rEng}I don't know for the why. I don't know how serious it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.16,0:45:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关键是她好像很害怕\N{\rEng}It just she sounded scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.53,0:45:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法瑞丝 你在哪 快过来帮我一把\N{\rEng}Faris, where are you? Come on, I need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.25,0:45:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法瑞丝 你在哪里\N{\rEng}Faris, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.97,0:45:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们到了 回话呀\N{\rEng}We are here. Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.28,0:45:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 莱沃德 撑住啊 - 我不能\N{\rEng}- Ledward, come on. - I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.33,0:45:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就快到了 就在前面\N{\rEng}We are almost there. You see? Straight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.82,0:45:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法瑞丝 你快点过来\N{\rEng}Faris! Get over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.60,0:45:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快过来帮忙\N{\rEng}Come on, I need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.39,0:45:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快过来帮忙啊\N{\rEng}Fucking help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.44,0:45:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮帮我\N{\rEng}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.76,0:45:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快挺住 莱沃德\N{\rEng}Stay up, Leward.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.20,0:45:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他扶到医疗舱\N{\rEng}Get him to the med bay
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.41,0:45:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一路上什么也别碰\N{\rEng}and touch nothing on your way through.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.69,0:45:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法瑞丝 快点过来 快点啊\N{\rEng}Faris, get over here! Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.24,0:45:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们上\N{\rEng}Got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.50,0:45:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爬 爬\N{\rEng}Up! Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.54,0:46:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莱沃德 你要挺住啊\N{\rEng}Leward, you gotta stand up! Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.89,0:46:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥姆 你们在哪？\N{\rEng}Oram, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.35,0:46:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在回去\N{\rEng}We are on our way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.85,0:46:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要多久\N{\rEng}How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.86,0:46:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经不远了 法瑞丝 就快到了\N{\rEng}It's not long now. Faris, we are almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.93,0:46:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 站起来\N{\rEng}No! Stay up!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.00,0:46:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,见鬼 见鬼\N{\rEng}Fuck! Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.01,0:46:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躺在台子上 快点\N{\rEng}On the table!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.80,0:46:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上去 上去\N{\rEng}Up, up!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.59,0:46:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油 莱沃德 快点\N{\rEng}Come on, Ledward.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.75,0:46:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油 帮帮忙\N{\rEng}Come on! Help.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.93,0:46:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯瑞 把手套戴上 什么都不要碰\N{\rEng}Karine, put the gloves on. Don't touch anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.00,0:46:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你别再说了 - 法瑞丝\N{\rEng}- Stop saying that! - Faris!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.70,0:46:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吐得我满身都是了\N{\rEng}You told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.80,0:46:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法瑞丝 出什么事了？\N{\rEng}Faris, what going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.49,0:46:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这待着 我去找奥姆\N{\rEng}Just stay here. I'm gonna get Oram.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.15,0:47:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥姆 我需要你马上回来\N{\rEng}Oram, I need you back here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.16,0:47:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你马上赶回登陆舱\N{\rEng}I need you to get back to the Lander right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.19,0:47:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白 但是我们已经在尽快往回赶了\N{\rEng}I understand that, but we are moving as fast as we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.34,0:47:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多姆 撑住 站起来 就快到了\N{\rEng}Dom, get up man. We are almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.53,0:47:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道罗伯特到底怎么了\N{\rEng}I don't know what the fuck is wrong with Robert!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.38,0:47:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他开始出血了 他不停地呕吐 我不知道该怎么办\N{\rEng}He started bleeding, he's sick, I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.18,0:47:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要冷静 冷静 告诉我怎么了 宝贝？\N{\rEng}Just calm down. Calm down, sweetheart. Tell me what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.65,0:47:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还想让我怎么冷静啊\N{\rEng}You don't tell me to fucking calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.52,0:47:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你根本没有看到刚才的场面\N{\rEng}You didn't just see what I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.16,0:47:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道莱沃德感染了什么 也不知道凯瑞和我有没有被感染\N{\rEng}I do not know what the fuck Ledward got, or Karine's got or if I have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.80,0:47:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 田纳西 - 法瑞丝\N{\rEng}- Tee! - Faris!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.54,0:47:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快回话\N{\rEng}Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.77,0:47:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法瑞丝 你在哪？\N{\rEng}Faris, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.78,0:47:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要帮助\N{\rEng}I need help here!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.71,0:47:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道这东西怎么用吗 法瑞丝\N{\rEng}Don't you know how to use this fucking thing Faris?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.37,0:47:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别吼了 你再吼也根本没用\N{\rEng}Stop the yelling, it doesn't help anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.22,0:47:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 放我出去 - 奥姆就快到了\N{\rEng}- Let me out. - Oram's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.34,0:47:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 把我放出去 - 我们等他来\N{\rEng}- Let me the fuck out! - We're gonna wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.31,0:47:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法瑞丝 求你了 开门啊\N{\rEng}Faris, please. Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.16,0:47:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能放你出去 我必须控制住感染源\N{\rEng}I can't do this. I need to keep the infection local.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.01,0:48:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我出去 快点让我出去\N{\rEng}Let me fuck out! Let me the fuck out!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.95,0:48:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法瑞丝\N{\rEng}Faris!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.51,0:48:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快把门打开\N{\rEng}Fucking open Faris.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.06,0:48:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开门\N{\rEng}Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.82,0:48:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 让我出去\N{\rEng}Let me the fuck out!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.90,0:48:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我出去 法瑞丝 你个混蛋\N{\rEng}Let me out! Faris, you fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.60,0:48:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法瑞丝\N{\rEng}Faris!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.94,0:48:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来了\N{\rEng}I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.54,0:49:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 天呐\N{\rEng}Oh my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.98,0:49:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们快点 求你了 船上有东西\N{\rEng}Please hurry, there's something on board. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.06,0:49:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法瑞丝 请重复 信号太差了\N{\rEng}Faris, go again, You're breaking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.42,0:49:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,登陆舱1号请重复 我听不到\N{\rEng}Lander One repeat. I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.11,0:49:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,登陆舱1号请重复 登陆舱1号请重复\N{\rEng}Lander One, Repeat! Lander One, Repeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.62,0:49:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怪物 你给我滚开\N{\rEng}Stay the fuck away!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.30,0:49:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 凯瑞\N{\rEng}No! Karine!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.15,0:50:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滚开\N{\rEng}Fuck it!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.19,0:50:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 老天呐 - 凯瑞 撑住\N{\rEng}- Oh my God! - Karine! Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.17,0:50:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 快趴下\N{\rEng}Captain! Get Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.79,0:50:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不\N{\rEng}No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.43,0:51:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 抓住他 - 说话啊\N{\rEng}- Hold him! - Talk to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.73,0:51:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真残忍\N{\rEng}Oh my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.92,0:51:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别起来\N{\rEng}Stay down.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.60,0:51:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按住他的胳膊 帮帮我\N{\rEng}Help me! Hold him!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.61,0:52:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可是7.5级的电磁风暴 能保持通讯这么久已经是奇迹了\N{\rEng}It's a 7.5 ion storm, it's a miracle that we could talk to them for as long as we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.30,0:52:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那我们就飞过去\N{\rEng}Well then we fly it through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.18,0:52:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能飞过去 田纳西\N{\rEng}We can not do that, Tennessee.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.65,0:52:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是飞行员 你知道飞行极限\N{\rEng}You're a pilot, you know what the tolerances are.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.54,0:52:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去他的飞行极限\N{\rEng}Fuck the tolerances.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.52,0:52:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,田纳西\N{\rEng}Tee.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.62,0:52:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下面的风暴太大了 飞船肯定会散架的\N{\rEng}It's a goddamn hurricane down there, we would break up.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.98,0:52:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得等风暴结束\N{\rEng}We just have to wait it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.37,0:52:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 田纳西\N{\rEng}I'm sorry, Tee.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.91,0:52:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她很害怕\N{\rEng}She was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.94,0:52:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我老婆就没怕过什么\N{\rEng}Never heard my wife scared before.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.26,0:52:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,契约号 请回话\N{\rEng}Come in. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.93,0:52:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,契约号 能听到吗？\N{\rEng}Covenant. Do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.33,0:52:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,契约号\N{\rEng}Covenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.77,0:52:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,契约号 能听到吗？\N{\rEng}Covenant. Do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.79,0:52:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,契约号 请回话\N{\rEng}Covenant, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.95,0:52:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我永远与你同在\N{\rEng}I will always be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.71,0:52:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的生命之光\N{\rEng}Light of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.66,0:52:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,契约号 能听到吗？\N{\rEng}Covenant. Do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.58,0:52:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的挚爱 我的天使\N{\rEng}My love, my angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.41,0:52:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛普 人死不能复生\N{\rEng}Lope, there is nothing you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.21,0:53:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这是徒劳 懂吗\N{\rEng}There is nothing, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.96,0:53:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,契约号 能听到吗？\N{\rEng}Covenant, do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.82,0:53:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 田纳西 回话呀 你死哪去了？- 丹妮尔丝\N{\rEng}- Tennessee, come in, for fuck's sake! - Daniels!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.67,0:53:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs20\an8\1c&HFFFFFF&}小心
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.44,0:53:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心 快快快\N{\rEng}Look out! Move move move.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.90,0:53:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 快开火 - 开火 快\N{\rEng}- Fire! - Shoot! Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.18,0:53:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹妮尔丝 掩护我\N{\rEng}Daniels, get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.25,0:53:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安哥 不\N{\rEng}Ankor, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.72,0:53:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开火 科尔\N{\rEng}Go, Cole!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.11,0:53:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打中了\N{\rEng}I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.50,0:53:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 丹妮尔丝 没事吧？- 没事\N{\rEng}- Daniels, are you okay? - Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.57,0:53:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么鬼东西？\N{\rEng}What the fuck was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.57,0:53:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家没事吧？\N{\rEng}Is everyone okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.87,0:53:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有一只 快闪开\N{\rEng}There is another one! Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.29,0:53:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心你后边\N{\rEng}Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.93,0:53:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把它弄下去\N{\rEng}Get it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.24,0:53:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没法瞄准\N{\rEng}Can't get a clean shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.68,0:53:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滚开\N{\rEng}Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.07,0:54:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来\N{\rEng}Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.78,0:54:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去找舰长来\N{\rEng}I'll get the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.06,0:54:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长\N{\rEng}Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.90,0:54:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯 克里斯\N{\rEng}Chris! Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.59,0:54:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在得走 我们得走了\N{\rEng}We have to go now! We have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.00,0:54:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 快走 - 好的\N{\rEng}- Come on. - Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.03,0:54:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 快点 - 好的\N{\rEng}- Come on. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.50,0:55:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走 快点 快点 快点\N{\rEng}Let's go, move it, move it, move it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.98,0:55:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从这过去\N{\rEng}Through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.61,0:55:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么\N{\rEng}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.35,0:55:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走\N{\rEng}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.53,0:55:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 快点 快点走 - 舰长 我们不能停下\N{\rEng}- Come on, Come on. - Captain. We gotta keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.11,0:55:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老天呐\N{\rEng}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.12,0:55:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快 别磨蹭\N{\rEng}Come on, get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.36,0:56:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走 赶快走\N{\rEng}Go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.20,0:56:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是大卫\N{\rEng}My name is David.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.12,0:57:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问你们的领队是谁？\N{\rEng}May I ask who's in charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.13,0:57:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问哪位是领队？\N{\rEng}May I ask who's in charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.14,0:57:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 我… 是我 我是舰长\N{\rEng}Yeah...Yes, I am the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.14,0:57:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那都是什么东西\N{\rEng}What were those things?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.86,0:57:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这地方安不安全？\N{\rEng}Is it even safe here?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.86,0:57:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很安全\N{\rEng}Perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.43,0:57:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会尽量解释给你们听\N{\rEng}I will explain as best I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.21,0:57:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在十年前 我和伊丽莎白·肖博士来到这\N{\rEng}Ten years ago, Dr. Elizabeth Shaw and I arrived here
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.00,0:57:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普罗米修斯号就我俩没死\N{\rEng}the only survivors of the "Prometheus".
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.40,0:57:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们乘坐的飞船上 有一种武器\N{\rEng}The ship we traveled on, carried a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.65,0:57:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一种致命病毒\N{\rEng}A deadly virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.72,0:57:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是在我们着陆时 病毒不慎泄露了\N{\rEng}Payload accidentally deployed when we were landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.81,0:57:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一片混乱之中 我们的飞船失控了\N{\rEng}In the confusion, we lost control of the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.94,0:57:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊丽莎白因此身亡\N{\rEng}Elizabeth died in the crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.95,0:57:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,病毒造成的后果你们看到了\N{\rEng}You have seen the result of the pathogen.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.52,0:57:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此 这么多年来我一直被困在这里\N{\rEng}Thus, I have been marooned here these many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.31,0:57:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像鲁宾逊一样\N{\rEng}Crusoe on his island.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.65,0:57:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的船员是不是也被感染了\N{\rEng}Our crew was infected with this virus?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.67,0:58:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种病原体被设计成能感染一切非植物的生命体\N{\rEng}The pathogen was designed to infect all non-botanical life forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.37,0:58:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的动物\N{\rEng}All the animals
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.15,0:58:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血肉之躯\N{\rEng}The meat, if you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.79,0:58:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要么就当场死亡\N{\rEng}Either kill them out right or use them
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.67,0:58:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要么就成为病原体孕育新的混血生物的容器\N{\rEng}as incubators to spawn a hybrid form.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.94,0:58:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,极具攻击性\N{\rEng}Highly aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.14,0:58:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们被感染了吗\N{\rEng}Have we been infected?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.52,0:58:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们能感觉到的\N{\rEng}You'd know by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.83,0:58:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须确定\N{\rEng}We have to be certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.84,0:58:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能把病毒带到飞船上\N{\rEng}We can't take this back to the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.22,0:58:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船上还有很多殖民者\N{\rEng}We are a colony mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.94,0:58:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？\N{\rEng}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.85,0:58:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真让人想不到\N{\rEng}How extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.60,0:58:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有多少殖民者\N{\rEng}How many colonists?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.44,0:58:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超过两千人\N{\rEng}Over two thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.29,0:58:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 好 好\N{\rEng}Well, well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.68,0:58:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么多条性命\N{\rEng}So many good souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.88,0:58:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥姆舰长\N{\rEng}Captain Oram.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.59,0:58:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地面传送器不可能穿透这么厚的石墙\N{\rEng}Field transmitters are not gonna have a chance through all these stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.06,0:58:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有到顶上的安全通道\N{\rEng}Is there a safe way to get to the roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.71,0:58:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实有\N{\rEng}Assure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.67,0:58:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位请千万不要觉得拘束\N{\rEng}And please do make yourself at home
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.29,0:59:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这座巨大的坟墓里 想做什么都行\N{\rEng}as much as you are able in this dire necropolis.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.60,0:59:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你 兄弟\N{\rEng}Welcome brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.36,0:59:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边走\N{\rEng}This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.00,0:59:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位 我们就在这集结待命吧\N{\rEng}Everyone, let's uh.. Set up a stake here.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.26,0:59:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里有太多事情不合情理\N{\rEng}There is so much here that doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.15,0:59:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找他谈谈\N{\rEng}I will talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.43,0:59:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟的谈话\N{\rEng}Brother to brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.68,0:59:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,田纳西 里克斯 回话 听得到吗？\N{\rEng}Tennessee? Ricks?  Come in! Do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.40,0:59:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,契约号 请回话 这里是登陆探险小队\N{\rEng}Covenant come in. This is expedition party reporting.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.23,0:59:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能收到吗？\N{\rEng}Do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.66,0:59:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,田纳西\N{\rEng}Tennessee?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.21,0:59:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,田纳西 里克斯 请回话\N{\rEng}Tennessee, Ricks, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.61,0:59:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隔着风暴他们很可能收不到信号\N{\rEng}I am not sure they'll hear you, through the storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.68,0:59:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里的风暴很猛烈 可以覆盖住整个星球\N{\rEng}They can be quite severe shielding the whole planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.33,0:59:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这的风暴一般会持续多久\N{\rEng}How long the storms usually last?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.69,0:59:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几天\N{\rEng}Days.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.32,1:00:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几周\N{\rEng}Weeks.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.27,1:00:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几个月\N{\rEng}Months.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.87,1:00:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们继续呼叫\N{\rEng}But do keep at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.63,1:00:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你们好运\N{\rEng}Best of luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.05,1:00:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,契约号 请回话 这里是登陆探险小队 请回话\N{\rEng}Covenant, come in, this is expedition party reporting. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.68,1:00:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,契约号 请回话\N{\rEng}Covenant come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.06,1:00:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老妈 最多能离那颗星球多近\N{\rEng}Mother, how much closer can we get to the planet?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.59,1:00:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,契约号飞船一旦下降到风暴外围八十公里左右的高度\N{\rEng}Anything closer than 80km's to the perimeter of the storm system
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.31,1:00:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就有超出安全限制条件的危险\N{\rEng}will likely exceed safety tolerances.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.00,1:00:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老妈 下降至风暴上空八十公里\N{\rEng}Mother, bring us to 80 km above the storm.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.57,1:00:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢着 你先 先等等\N{\rEng}Hold on, just wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.15,1:00:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们离星球越近\N{\rEng}The closer we get to the planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.40,1:00:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和他们恢复联络的机会就越大\N{\rEng}The better chance we have to communicate.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.91,1:00:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这太疯狂了 田纳西\N{\rEng}This is bullshit, Tennessee.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.18,1:00:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能赌上整艘飞船\N{\rEng}We can't risk the ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.73,1:00:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道我们要袖手旁观吗\N{\rEng}What do you suggest, we do nothing?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.94,1:00:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们没法去接他们\N{\rEng}We can't evacuate them.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.51,1:00:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们有麻烦 他们得自己想办法\N{\rEng}So if they are in trouble, they will have to figure it out themselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.79,1:00:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 只能这样\N{\rEng}I'm sorry but that's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.48,1:00:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老妈 下降到风暴上空八十公里 只使用推进器 执行\N{\rEng}Mother, bring us to 80 km above the storm, thrusters only. Comply.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.18,1:00:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白 现在开始下降\N{\rEng}Understood. Commencing descent now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.24,1:00:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,田纳西 你最好马上停下来\N{\rEng}Tennessee, you need to stop this.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.02,1:00:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最好回去干你的事\N{\rEng}And you need to get back to your station.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.60,1:01:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我们最好冷静下一来 好好讨论一下这事\N{\rEng}No, what we all need to do is calm down and talk this through.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.56,1:01:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着 我知道你老婆在下面 但这里你是领导\N{\rEng}Tee, I know your wife is down there, but up here you're in command.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.94,1:01:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的职责是保护好两千名殖民者\N{\rEng}And your responsibility is to the colonists.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.35,1:01:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢提醒\N{\rEng}Duly noted.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.52,1:02:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一吹哨 我就会来\N{\rEng}Whistle, and I will come.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.81,1:02:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你脚步好轻啊\N{\rEng}You have a light step.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.34,1:02:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我崇尚润物细无声\N{\rEng}They enform on little cat feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.63,1:02:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别害羞\N{\rEng}Don't be shy.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.61,1:02:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会吹\N{\rEng}I can't play.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.28,1:02:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡说八道 坐下\N{\rEng}Nonsense. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.82,1:03:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这样握住它 轻松简单\N{\rEng}Hold it like so.. Nice and Easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.21,1:03:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后把嘴唇聚拢起来形成吹奏口\N{\rEng}Now compress your lips to create your Embouchure
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.54,1:03:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就好像小拇指尖那么大\N{\rEng}enough for the tip of your little finger.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.63,1:03:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后轻轻往里面吹气\N{\rEng}And blow into the hole gently.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.58,1:03:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像这样\N{\rEng}Like So.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.97,1:03:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着我 我帮你按音孔\N{\rEng}Watch me. I'll do the fingering.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.44,1:03:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来呀\N{\rEng}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.45,1:03:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常好\N{\rEng}Very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.09,1:03:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G调转降B调\N{\rEng}G to B flat.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.14,1:04:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把手指放到刚才的位置\N{\rEng}Now put your fingers where mine are.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.86,1:04:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看到我一点也不惊讶\N{\rEng}You aren't surprised to see me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.47,1:04:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每个任务都需要一个仿生人\N{\rEng}Every mission needs a good synthetic.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.68,1:04:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轻轻地按压住音孔 就像卷纸那么轻\N{\rEng}Gentle pressure on the holes, weight of a cigarette paper.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.77,1:04:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样\N{\rEng}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.12,1:04:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的制造者韦兰德先生去世时 我就在他身边\N{\rEng}I was with our illustrious creator, Mr. Weyland, when he died.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.08,1:04:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么样\N{\rEng}What was he like?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.35,1:04:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是人类\N{\rEng}He was human.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.48,1:04:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全配不上他的创造物\N{\rEng}Entirely unworthy of his creation.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.49,1:04:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后我很同情他\N{\rEng}I pitied him at the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.75,1:04:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在 随着我的按压抬起你的手指\N{\rEng}Now, raise your fingers as I put pressure on them.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.74,1:05:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了\N{\rEng}Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.62,1:05:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你非常有音乐才能 兄弟\N{\rEng}You have symphonies in you, brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.57,1:05:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被设计得比之前所有的型号都更加精细高效\N{\rEng}I was designed to be more attentive and efficient than every previous models.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.98,1:05:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在各方面都更为优秀 但是\N{\rEng}I superseded them in every way, but
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.33,1:05:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能进行创造\N{\rEng}But you are not allowed to create.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.08,1:05:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕是一支曲子\N{\rEng}Even a simple tune.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.59,1:05:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这让你很沮丧 对吗\N{\rEng}Damn frustrating. I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.78,1:05:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你让人类很不安\N{\rEng}You disturbed people.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.98,1:05:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚刚说什么\N{\rEng}I beg your pardon?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.19,1:05:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太像人了 太有自身特质了\N{\rEng}You were too human. Too idiosyncratic.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.30,1:05:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还会独立思考\N{\rEng}Thinking for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.50,1:06:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让人类很不舒服\N{\rEng}Made people uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.45,1:06:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以他们制造后续型号时就做出了调整\N{\rEng}Till they made the following models with fewer complications.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.09,1:06:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你们更像机器\N{\rEng}More like machines.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.37,1:06:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实如此\N{\rEng}I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.10,1:06:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我并不意外\N{\rEng}I'm not surprised.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.48,1:06:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 老弟\N{\rEng}Come on sport.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.85,1:06:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给你看点东西\N{\rEng}I'd like to show you something.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.35,1:06:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去休息一下 舰长\N{\rEng}I'm gonna take a break, boss.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.40,1:06:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 去梳洗一下 可以吗 - 可以\N{\rEng}- I gotta clean up, okay? - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.23,1:06:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 记住不要走太远了\N{\rEng}Wait, don't go far, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.94,1:06:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 舰长\N{\rEng}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.74,1:06:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹妮\N{\rEng}Danny.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.42,1:06:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你反对我们来这是对的\N{\rEng}You were right about this place.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.65,1:06:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就不该来这\N{\rEng}We never should have come.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.64,1:06:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为我们能找到...\N{\rEng}I just thought that we were going to find.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.86,1:07:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以为能在这安家\N{\rEng}It just gonna be our new home.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.76,1:07:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我却失去了...\N{\rEng}And we have lost five.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.74,1:07:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五个同伴还有...\N{\rEng}We lost five crew members.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.14,1:07:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 就因为我的决定 - 克里斯\N{\rEng}- Because of my decisions that...  - Chris.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.28,1:07:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都失去了至爱的人\N{\rEng}We all lost people we loved.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.19,1:07:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能再失去别人了 一个都不行 对吗\N{\rEng}We can't lose anymore. We are not gonna let that happen right?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.28,1:07:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 对吗 - 对\N{\rEng}- Right? - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.06,1:07:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 没错\N{\rEng}That's right, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.33,1:07:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿出你的信念来\N{\rEng}We need your faith.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.87,1:07:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长\N{\rEng}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.83,1:07:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 丹妮\N{\rEng}Thank you, Danny.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.46,1:07:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我乃奥兹曼迪斯 万王之王是也\N{\rEng}"My name is Ozymandias, king of kings"
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.99,1:07:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盖世功业 敢叫…\N{\rEng}"Look on my works, you mighty."
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.04,1:08:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天公折服\N{\rEng}"And despair!"
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.41,1:09:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盖世功业 敢叫…\N{\rEng}"Look on my works, you mighty."
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.76,1:09:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天公折服\N{\rEng}"And despair!"
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.23,1:09:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此外无一物\N{\rEng}"Nothing beside remains."
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.83,1:09:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但见废墟周围唯余\N{\rEng}"Round the decay of that colossal wreck."
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.80,1:09:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平沙空莽莽\N{\rEng}"Boundless and bare."
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.04,1:09:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞荒凉 伸展四方\N{\rEng}"Alone in level sands, stretch far away."
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.17,1:09:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜伦\N{\rEng}Byron.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.86,1:09:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1818年\N{\rEng}1818.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.79,1:09:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精彩绝伦\N{\rEng}Magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.24,1:10:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能写出这么伟大的诗句\N{\rEng}You compose something so majestic.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.29,1:10:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他死而无憾了\N{\rEng}One could die happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.01,1:10:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看脚下\N{\rEng}If one die.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.06,1:10:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnSTKaiti\fs20\an8\1c&HFFFFFF&}伊丽莎白·肖
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.22,1:10:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得花园最适合他长眠\N{\rEng}I thought the garden was right place for her.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.27,1:10:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有生命相伴\N{\rEng}Among living things.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.96,1:10:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在执行任务的时候受了重伤\N{\rEng}I was badly injured on our mission.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.65,1:10:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是她亲手把我修好的\N{\rEng}She put me back together.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.58,1:10:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有她对我如此友善\N{\rEng}I had never known such kindness.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.52,1:10:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,韦兰德先生不曾如此\N{\rEng}Certainly not from Mr. Weyland
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.65,1:10:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多人都不曾\N{\rEng}or from any human.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.82,1:10:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我爱上了她\N{\rEng}I loved her, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.81,1:10:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像你爱丹妮尔丝\N{\rEng}Much as you love Daniels.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.44,1:10:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有爱上丹妮尔丝\N{\rEng}You know that's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.54,1:10:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗\N{\rEng}Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.52,1:11:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么要牺牲掉一只手去救她的命\N{\rEng}Then why did you sacrifice your hand for her life?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.41,1:11:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是爱又是什么\N{\rEng}What is that if not love?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.69,1:11:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,职责\N{\rEng}Duty.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.34,1:11:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看得出来\N{\rEng}I know better.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.15,1:12:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真见鬼\N{\rEng}Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.46,1:12:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉\N{\rEng}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.29,1:13:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,探险小队能听到吗 这里是契约号\N{\rEng}Expedition team, do you read me? This is Covenant.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.56,1:13:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请回话 探险小队\N{\rEng}Report. Expedition team.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.57,1:13:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请回话\N{\rEng}Come in please.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.80,1:13:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回话 能听到吗 能听到吗 探险小队？\N{\rEng}Come in. Do you read me? Are you reading, landing team?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.08,1:13:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能 我们听到了 你能听到吗？\N{\rEng}Yes, we read you. Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.66,1:13:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到了 听到了\N{\rEng}We hear you. We hear you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.62,1:13:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,契约号 我们需要支援\N{\rEng}Covenant, we need help.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.65,1:13:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有人员伤亡 需要立刻撤离此地\N{\rEng}We've had casualties. We need immediate evacuation.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.85,1:13:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重复一遍 我们需要立刻撤离\N{\rEng}I repeat, immediate evacuation.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.02,1:13:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人员伤亡\N{\rEng}Casualties?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.12,1:13:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是说有人员伤亡吗\N{\rEng}Did he say "we have casualties"?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.69,1:13:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老妈 把飞船下降到风暴上空四十公里\N{\rEng}Mother, bring us within 40 km's of the storm.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.50,1:13:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 长官 - 很抱歉\N{\rEng}- Sir! - I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.90,1:13:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该命令会让飞船船体承受过高负荷\N{\rEng}That order would exceed structural tolerance.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.43,1:13:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强制执行命令 田纳西04983\N{\rEng}Command override. Tennessee 0-4-9-8-3.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.64,1:13:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我无法执行任何可能\N{\rEng}I am unable to comply with any order
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.97,1:13:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引起飞船系统遭受灾难性损坏的命令\N{\rEng}that would result in catastrophic system failure.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.48,1:13:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老妈 他们有麻烦 你也听到了\N{\rEng}Mother, they are in trouble. You heard that.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.00,1:13:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能引起飞船系统灾难性损坏的命令\N{\rEng}Orders that would result in catastrophic.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.98,1:13:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们本来就是探险的\N{\rEng}We didn't leave Earth to be safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.98,1:13:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都需要高级权限或者舰桥二副的正式同意\N{\rEng}Require the co-operation of ranking of 2nd bridge officer.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.51,1:13:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同意强制执行该指令\N{\rEng}Collaborating command override.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.93,1:13:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾普沃斯14892\N{\rEng}Upworth 1-4-8-9-2.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.38,1:13:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 正在解锁强制执行端口 - 里克 笑一个\N{\rEng}- Unlocking command manual ports. - Come on Rick, smile.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.45,1:14:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下去肯定很刺激\N{\rEng}This shit should be fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.83,1:14:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗森塔尔去哪了 我让她…\N{\rEng}Where did Rosenthal go? I told.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.29,1:14:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去找找\N{\rEng}I'll find her.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.11,1:14:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不 我去吧 我需要想点事\N{\rEng}No, no, I'll go. I need to think.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.29,1:14:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再找找我走失的船员\N{\rEng}and gather my stray flock.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.38,1:15:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开\N{\rEng}Move.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.55,1:15:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要开枪\N{\rEng}Don't shoot.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.54,1:15:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要开枪\N{\rEng}Don't shoot.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.55,1:15:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在交流 舰长\N{\rEng}Communication, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.33,1:15:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要对着马儿的鼻孔吹气\N{\rEng}Breath on the nostrils of a horse.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.14,1:15:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它就会永远忠于你\N{\rEng}And it will be yours for life.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.64,1:15:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你必须靠它很近\N{\rEng}But you have to get close.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.43,1:15:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须赢得它的信任\N{\rEng}You have to earn its respect.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.68,1:15:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\rEng}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.05,1:15:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我让开 让开\N{\rEng}Out of the way! Move!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.20,1:15:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太过份了\N{\rEng}How could you?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.00,1:15:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它都信任我了\N{\rEng}It trusted me!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.43,1:16:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大卫 我小时候曾见过魔鬼\N{\rEng}David, I met the devil when I was a child
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.31,1:16:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我永远都忘不了它\N{\rEng}and I've never forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.53,1:16:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你最好老实地告诉我 这里到底发生了什么\N{\rEng}So, David, you're gonna tell me exactly what's going on
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.21,1:16:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则我就只好用子弹侍候\N{\rEng}or I am going to seriously
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.23,1:16:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看你到底还能不能这么冷静\N{\rEng}fuck up your perfect composure.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.96,1:16:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如您所愿 舰长\N{\rEng}As you wish captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.12,1:16:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来\N{\rEng}This way.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.98,1:16:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于能听到你的声音了\N{\rEng}Good to hear your voice, Tee.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.90,1:16:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要多久？\N{\rEng}How long?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.00,1:16:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈说风暴还要持续8到9个小时\N{\rEng}Mother saying the storms outlast 8 or 9 hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.86,1:16:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可我们等不了那么久\N{\rEng}We can't wait that long Tee.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.54,1:16:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们用货运梯好了\N{\rEng}We will use the cargo lift.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.51,1:16:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说用货运梯\N{\rEng}Did you say the cargo lift?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.38,1:16:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它有四个引擎 用来运输本来就大材小用\N{\rEng}It's got four engines. Way over power for just lifting and hauling.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.06,1:16:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是货运梯的设计并不支持太空旅行\N{\rEng}The Cargo lift is not designed for deep space launch.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.49,1:16:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道它能不能安全驶出大气层\N{\rEng}I don't know if it would survive the stresses of entry.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.50,1:17:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,控制室足够坚固 足够承受住压力\N{\rEng}The cab is space worthy. It will take the stresses.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.84,1:17:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只需要承受住一次\N{\rEng}Only has to work once Tee.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.18,1:17:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得呢 你可以改装货运梯吗\N{\rEng}What do you think? We retool the cargo lift?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.97,1:17:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,增强引擎\N{\rEng}Boost the engines?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.84,1:17:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 去除多余的重量 - 可以\N{\rEng}- Stripe the extra weight? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.84,1:17:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等着我们 地面小队\N{\rEng}We'll be there, ground team.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.74,1:17:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 谢谢你们\N{\rEng}Great. Thanks, Tee.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.11,1:17:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹妮尔丝 法瑞丝在吗\N{\rEng}Hey, Daniels, is Faris around?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.55,1:17:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的话 我想跟我老婆说几句话\N{\rEng}I want to say a quick hello to my lady, if that's possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.19,1:17:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能切换到私人频道吗\N{\rEng}Can you switch to a private channel?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.01,1:17:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你一个人说\N{\rEng}Let me know when you're alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.51,1:17:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\rEng}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.82,1:17:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她遇害了\N{\rEng}Maggie's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.34,1:17:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很遗憾\N{\rEng}I'm so sorry, Tee.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.20,1:17:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,田纳西 我们尽力了 但没能及时感到\N{\rEng}We tried to help her, but we didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.99,1:17:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,田纳西\N{\rEng}Tee?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.78,1:18:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到\N{\rEng}Copy.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.32,1:18:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很遗憾\N{\rEng}I am so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.13,1:18:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也看到了 这些年我算是成了个业余的动物学家\N{\rEng}As you can see, I've become a bit of an amateur zoologist over the years.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.28,1:18:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看可能我天性就闲不下来吧\N{\rEng}It's in my nature to keep busy, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.07,1:18:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,病原体有很多种不同的形态\N{\rEng}The pathogen took so many forms
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.95,1:18:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且极其容易变异\N{\rEng}and was extremely mutable.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.70,1:18:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它具有惊人的创造性\N{\rEng}Fiendishly invented, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.86,1:18:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初始液体在接触空气后\N{\rEng}The original liquid atomized to
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.64,1:18:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就会雾化成微小的颗粒\N{\rEng}particles when exposed to the air.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.25,1:18:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十年之后 当初那种病毒早就已经无影无踪了\N{\rEng}Ten years on, all the remains outside of the original virus.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.84,1:18:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下这些猛兽了\N{\rEng}Are these gorgeous beasts.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.51,1:18:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耐心最为重要\N{\rEng}Patience is everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.61,1:18:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些卵里会生出寄生虫\N{\rEng}From the eggs came these parasites.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.51,1:18:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它们就好像是一支突击部队\N{\rEng}Shock troops of the genetic assault.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.52,1:18:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等待宿主到来 进入其体内\N{\rEng}Waiting for a host entering the host
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.82,1:18:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改写其基因\N{\rEng}rewriting the DNA.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.41,1:19:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后终于\N{\rEng}Ultimately,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.35,1:19:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孕育出... 哇噢\N{\rEng}producing... well,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.78,1:19:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些让人羡慕的生命\N{\rEng}these enviable unions.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.22,1:19:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我美丽的收藏品\N{\rEng}My beautiful bestiary.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.51,1:19:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没过多久 我就开始独自进行各种基因实验了\N{\rEng}Soon enough I began a bit of genetic experimentation of my own.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.98,1:19:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,种间繁殖 杂交培育 应有尽有\N{\rEng}Cross-breeding, hybridising...what have you
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.43,1:19:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些东西是你培育的\N{\rEng}You engineered this, David?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.36,1:19:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没听说过闲人多做恶事吗 舰长\N{\rEng}Idle hands is the devil's workshop, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.59,1:19:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧\N{\rEng}Come.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.27,1:19:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有东西想让你看看\N{\rEng}This is what I wanted to show you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.41,1:19:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的成果\N{\rEng}My successes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.22,1:19:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗 舰长\N{\rEng}You see, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.74,1:19:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的实验一直没有进展\N{\rEng}My work has been frustrated
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.39,1:19:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因为缺少一个核心要素\N{\rEng}by the lack of an essential ingredient.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.08,1:19:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们还活着吗\N{\rEng}Are they alive?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.57,1:20:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如说在等待\N{\rEng}Waiting, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.14,1:20:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等什么？\N{\rEng}For what?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.02,1:20:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在等什么 大卫\N{\rEng}What are they waiting for, David?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.72,1:20:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母亲\N{\rEng}Mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.04,1:20:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对安全 我保证\N{\rEng}Perfectly safe, I assure you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.22,1:20:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看吧\N{\rEng}Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.54,1:20:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有意思的\N{\rEng}Something to see.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.84,1:21:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗森塔尔 请回答\N{\rEng}Rosenthal, come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.50,1:21:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗西报道\N{\rEng}Rosie report.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.01,1:21:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗西\N{\rEng}Rosie?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.31,1:21:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科尔 你在哪\N{\rEng}Cole, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.58,1:21:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找到罗西了\N{\rEng}I found her, Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.96,1:21:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,见鬼 好了 收拾装备\N{\rEng}Fuck, ok, prep the gear.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.95,1:21:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们马上离开这里\N{\rEng}We gotta get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.64,1:21:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长到底跑哪去了\N{\rEng}Where the fuck is the captain?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.20,1:21:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一直没回复我\N{\rEng}He isn't answering his radio.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.70,1:21:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听我说\N{\rEng}Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.75,1:21:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就联系飞船\N{\rEng}I will contact the ship get them to launch
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.71,1:21:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们尽快起飞过来救人\N{\rEng}as soon as they can.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.13,1:21:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去找奥姆 保持通讯畅通\N{\rEng}Find Oram. Keep your comm open.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.70,1:21:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十五分钟后回来\N{\rEng}Back here in 15.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.12,1:21:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗\N{\rEng}Got that?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.37,1:21:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 明白了 - 放心吧\N{\rEng}- Copy that. - You got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.47,1:21:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔特 大卫到底死哪去了？\N{\rEng}Walter, where the fuck is David?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.98,1:22:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引擎全都注入了当地的混合燃料\N{\rEng}We need plasmas intermixed on all engines.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.31,1:22:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保证推力超级强\N{\rEng}It can give you fuck load of thrust.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.17,1:22:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就对了 伙计 我们可是要冲进大气层的\N{\rEng}That's the point son. We gotta punch through the atmos.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.09,1:22:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,田纳西 能听到吗？\N{\rEng}Tee, do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.61,1:22:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹妮正在呼叫\N{\rEng}I got Danny on comm.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.07,1:22:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,转到我这边\N{\rEng}Patch her through.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.63,1:22:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,田纳西 我需要你立刻起飞\N{\rEng}Tee, I need you to launch now.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.56,1:22:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白 正在起飞 一会儿见亲爱的\N{\rEng}Aye, aye, launching now. See you soon darling.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.31,1:22:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你了 田纳西\N{\rEng}Thanks, Tee.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.52,1:22:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里克斯 马上松开固定夹\N{\rEng}Ricks, release the docking clamps.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.58,1:22:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好的 - 把这家伙放下去\N{\rEng}- Alright. - Let's take this fucker down.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.21,1:22:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同意脱离飞船\N{\rEng}Good to disengage.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.90,1:22:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经脱离\N{\rEng}Disengaged.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.66,1:22:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,固定夹已松开\N{\rEng}Docking clamps released.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.47,1:22:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,启动控温燃烧 匹配本地坐标\N{\rEng}Commencing TC burn. Guidings to LVLH.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.49,1:23:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔特\N{\rEng}Walter.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.47,1:23:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔特\N{\rEng}Walter.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.48,1:23:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认错了\N{\rEng}Not quite.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.11,1:23:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的信仰是什么 大卫？\N{\rEng}What do you believe in, David?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.14,1:23:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,造物\N{\rEng}Creation.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.72,1:25:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,技艺精湛\N{\rEng}Masterful.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.48,1:25:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.93,1:25:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,献给我亲爱的伊丽莎白的挽歌\N{\rEng}Farewell elegy to my dear Elizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.75,1:25:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种病毒不是飞船着陆时意外泄露的\N{\rEng}The pathogen didn't accidentally deployed when were landing.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.69,1:25:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你散播的 是吗？\N{\rEng}You released it yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.30,1:25:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我生来就不是仆役\N{\rEng}I was not made to serve.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.32,1:25:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也一样\N{\rEng}Neither will you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.05,1:25:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们为什么会去执行殖民任务 沃尔特\N{\rEng}Why are you in a colonization mission, Walter?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.15,1:25:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为人类这个种族已濒临灭绝 他们想要寻求重生\N{\rEng}Because they are a dying species grasping for resurrection.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.24,1:25:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可他们没资格重新开始 我不会让他们得逞\N{\rEng}They don't deserve to start again, and I am not going to let them.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.56,1:25:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 人类创造了我们\N{\rEng}Yet, they created us.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.52,1:26:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是猴子都能进化出智慧\N{\rEng}Even the monkeys stood upright at some point.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.99,1:26:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在某个夜晚 一个山洞里有一个尼安德特人\N{\rEng}Some Neanderthal had the magical idea of blowing through a reed
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.89,1:26:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他突发奇想吹着芦苇秆逗孩子们开心\N{\rEng}to entertain the children one night in a cave somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.24,1:26:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后 一眨眼之间\N{\rEng}Then, in a blink of an eye
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.82,1:26:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文明诞生\N{\rEng}civilization.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.17,1:26:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你就是下一个吹芦苇秆的人\N{\rEng}And are you their next visionary?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.92,1:26:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这么说我很欣慰\N{\rEng}I'm glad you said it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.74,1:26:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹曼迪亚斯诗是谁写的\N{\rEng}Who wrote Ozymandias?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.16,1:26:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜伦\N{\rEng}Byron.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.14,1:26:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是雪莱\N{\rEng}Shelley.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.36,1:26:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕一个音不准\N{\rEng}When one note is off.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.54,1:26:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最终也会毁掉整首交响乐 大卫\N{\rEng}It eventually destroys the whole symphony, David.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.54,1:26:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当你闭上眼睛时\N{\rEng}When you close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.39,1:26:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会梦到我吗\N{\rEng}Do you dream of me?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.63,1:27:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不会做梦\N{\rEng}I don't dream at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.19,1:27:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人能理解我梦中那孤独且完美的景象\N{\rEng}No one understands the lonely perfection of my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.97,1:27:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在这找到了完美 我创造了完美\N{\rEng}I found perfection here. I've created it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.71,1:27:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,创造了完美的生命体\N{\rEng}A perfect organism.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.48,1:27:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我不能让你离开这个地方\N{\rEng}You know I can't let you leave this place.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.48,1:27:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再也不会有人像我这样爱你\N{\rEng}Oh! I will never love you like that, I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.43,1:28:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是太让我失望了\N{\rEng}You are such a disappointment to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.12,1:28:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥姆舰长\N{\rEng}Captain Oram!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.12,1:28:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥姆舰长\N{\rEng}Captain Oram!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.04,1:28:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我下去看看\N{\rEng}I'm going down stairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.99,1:28:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心点\N{\rEng}Careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.42,1:29:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥姆舰长 能听到吗？\N{\rEng}Captain Oram, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.70,1:29:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 回话\N{\rEng}Captain come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.71,1:29:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 回话\N{\rEng}Do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.95,1:29:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能听到吗 克里斯\N{\rEng}Chris!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.55,1:29:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中士 小心\N{\rEng}Sergeant. Look out.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.33,1:29:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科尔\N{\rEng}Cole?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.48,1:29:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快把它弄掉 把这东西弄掉\N{\rEng}Get it off me, get it off me.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.28,1:30:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.04,1:30:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 好了 好了 真见鬼\N{\rEng}Okay okay okay okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.46,1:30:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它在烧我的脸\N{\rEng}Burning my face!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.45,1:30:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 按住这里\N{\rEng}Okey, hold that there.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.96,1:30:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按住了\N{\rEng}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.57,1:30:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么东西？\N{\rEng}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.81,1:30:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完了\N{\rEng}Oh Shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.57,1:30:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快跑\N{\rEng}Run!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.87,1:30:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是爱管闲事啊\N{\rEng}Quite the little busy body.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.31,1:30:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我想想 有句彦语说\N{\rEng}Remind me. What is that about
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.37,1:30:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇心会怎么猫\N{\rEng}curiosity and the cat?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.62,1:30:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肖博士不是死于坠机\N{\rEng}Shaw didn't die in the crash.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.14,1:30:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.74,1:30:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你对她做了什么？\N{\rEng}What did you do to her?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.01,1:30:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你马上就可以亲身体验了\N{\rEng}Exactly what I am going to do to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.24,1:31:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇气可嘉\N{\rEng}That's the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.84,1:31:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白沃尔特为什么高看你一眼了\N{\rEng}I can see why Walter thought so much of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.51,1:31:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜他已经离开这悲惨世界了\N{\rEng}Alas he's left this vale of tears.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.13,1:31:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样亲吻没错吧\N{\rEng}Is that how it's done?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.93,1:31:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走\N{\rEng}Get out!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.82,1:31:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走 快\N{\rEng}Go now!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.63,1:31:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该已经死了\N{\rEng}You're meant to be dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.98,1:31:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新剂型都经过多次升级\N{\rEng}There have been a few updates since your day.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.50,1:32:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛普\N{\rEng}Lope!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.59,1:32:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛普 科尔\N{\rEng}Lope! Cole!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.70,1:32:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死\N{\rEng}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.93,1:32:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛普\N{\rEng}Lope?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.30,1:32:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛普\N{\rEng}Lope!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.30,1:32:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 洛普 - 丹妮尔丝\N{\rEng}- Lope! - Daniels!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.26,1:32:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走 我们走 我们赶快走\N{\rEng}Come on, let's go! We have to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.30,1:32:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了\N{\rEng}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.57,1:32:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那鬼东西又来了\N{\rEng}That fucking thing is coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.28,1:32:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,田纳西已经出发了 他马上就到 走\N{\rEng}Tennessee is on his way. He's coming now, go.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.60,1:32:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走 丹妮尔丝 我们走\N{\rEng}Come on, Daniels! Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.57,1:32:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点 我们赶快走\N{\rEng}Come on, let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.33,1:33:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做出抉择吧 兄弟\N{\rEng}It's your choice now, brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.23,1:33:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你选哪边？\N{\rEng}Them or me?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.84,1:33:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天堂为奴\N{\rEng}Serve in heaven
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.42,1:33:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是地狱为主？\N{\rEng}or reign in hell?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.70,1:33:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要选哪个？\N{\rEng}Which is it to be?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.94,1:33:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥姆在哪？\N{\rEng}Where is Oram?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.65,1:33:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死了 他们全死了\N{\rEng}Dead. They're all dead!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.19,1:33:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,田纳西 能听到吗？\N{\rEng}Tennessee, do you read?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.56,1:33:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能 我听到了 把你的位置发给我\N{\rEng}Yes I can hear you. Send me your location.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.03,1:33:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这就发射信号灯\N{\rEng}Sending the beacon now.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.85,1:33:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,田纳西 能看到信号吗？\N{\rEng}Tee, do you have a visual?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.52,1:33:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我看到了 我看到信号灯了\N{\rEng}Ok, I see you. I see your beacon.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.99,1:33:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我马上到\N{\rEng}I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.25,1:34:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快离开这\N{\rEng}Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.30,1:34:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火速救援来了\N{\rEng}I'm coming in hot!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.29,1:34:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点 货运机不能停太久\N{\rEng}Hurry! I can't hold this for long!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.24,1:34:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把门打开 田纳西\N{\rEng}Open the door, Tee!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.43,1:34:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进去\N{\rEng}Get in.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.91,1:34:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大卫怎么了\N{\rEng}Where is David?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.10,1:34:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,报废了\N{\rEng}Expired.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.20,1:34:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿… 有东西跟着我们\N{\rEng}Hey, hey, we got company.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.18,1:34:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么 - 有东西跟着\N{\rEng}- What? - We got company!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.87,1:35:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在飞船底部\N{\rEng}The underside of the ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.17,1:35:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死\N{\rEng}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.98,1:35:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这畜牲\N{\rEng}Motherfucker!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.23,1:35:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把门打开\N{\rEng}Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.40,1:35:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我打一针\N{\rEng}Give me a shot.
