Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.21,1:39:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你给他打太多镇静剂了\N{\rEng}I gave him pretty heavy sedative.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.51,1:39:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 老天啊 真可怜\N{\rEng}Oh Jesus, poor Lope.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.43,1:39:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 看起来就像歌剧魅影\N{\rEng}He looks like the Phantom of the Opera.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.17,1:39:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真看不出来你还喜欢音乐剧呢\N{\rEng}Didn't think you for a musical fan.
