Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.57,1:39:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是个护理员 他必须找真正的医生做皮肤再造手术\N{\rEng}I'm just a medic. He's gonna need reconstructive surgery by a real doctor.
