Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.18,1:40:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要谢谢你救了我的命\N{\rEng}Thank you for saving my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.90,1:40:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两次\N{\rEng}Again.
