Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.05,1:41:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概四小时后会重新上线\N{\rEng}She'll be back online at eight bells.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.75,1:41:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 多谢你了 田纳西\N{\rEng}All right. Thanks, Tee.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.05,1:41:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在是不是要喊你舰长了\N{\rEng}This mean I have to call you "Captain" now?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.97,1:41:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那当然\N{\rEng}I guess.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.61,1:42:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请注意\N{\rEng}Attention.
