Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.64,1:43:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请迅速从起居舱撤离\N{\rEng}Evacuate crew quarters immediately.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.05,1:44:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要\N{\rEng}No!
