Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.40,1:44:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B39已关闭\N{\rEng}B-39, closed.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.61,1:45:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔特\N{\rEng}Walter.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.73,1:45:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 它在哪？- 丹妮尔丝\N{\rEng}- Where is it? - Daniels.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.97,1:45:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来\N{\rEng}This way.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.09,1:45:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,田纳西 我们先选个战场吧\N{\rEng}Tee, let's choose our ground.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.77,1:45:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后把它引过来\N{\rEng}We'll bring it to us.
