Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.54,1:45:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B06和B05已关闭\N{\rEng}B-6, B-5 closed.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.91,1:46:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 沃尔特 它在哪\N{\rEng}Hey Walter where is it?
